```class Solution {
    public int minimumOneBitOperations(int n) {
        int res = 0;
        while ((n & 1) == 0) {
            n >>= 1;
            res++;
        }
        while (n > 0) {
            int i = Integer.highestOneBit(n);
            n ^= i;
            res++;
        }
        return res;
    }
}```
